11 Hetuduka, Sekkhattika
Hetuduka, Sekkhattika
19.
53Hetuṃ sekkhaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu nasekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
54Hetuṃ asekkhaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu naasekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
55Nahetuṃ nevasekkhanāsekkhaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nanahetu nanevasekkhanāsekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
